Name: Blankspace
About the game: Not sure what he's been doing the night before, Chris wakes up in a strange room, handcuffed to a pipe. He doesn't recognize the girl that wakes up next to him, but it seems they're both in a similar predicament. What's their story? Can they get out? - 3-8 hours of playtime - A story-rich, character-driven narrative - Choices that affect your relationship & ending - Multiple endings - Genres: mystery, puzzle, suspense, romance - Optional free H-patch - Available for Windows & Linux Nayru - Creator Xolf - Co-writing / Coding Assistance OddTillTheEnd - Music
